# Crontabs
### 'export DISPLAY=:0.0' is for making notifications with notify-send work

## Uppdate RSS feed
*/45 */4 * * *		export DISPLAY=:0.0; sh /home/mqx/.local/bin/cron/newsup

## Activate internet
@reboot			/usr/bin/NetworkManager -n

## Activate light
@reboot			/home/mqx/.local/bin/light_activation

## Activate calcurse reminders
@reboot			/usr/bin/sleep 12; export DISPLAY=:0.0; sh /home/mqx/.local/bin/calcurse_reminders || /usr/bin/notify-send "❗ Error opening calcurse_reminders ❗"

## Update packages
### for being sure internet connection is established we use 'sleep 12'
@reboot			/usr/bin/sleep 42; export DISPLAY=:0.0; sh /home/mqx/.local/bin/cron/checkup
